assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Toyo Tec Co.,Ltd. provides security services in Japan. The company offers machine, home, transportation, and facility security services. It provides mechanical security systems, surveillance cameras, resident, transport, crowd guards, entrance/exit management/employee ID cards, and fireproof and anti-theft safes; disaster prevention and energy saving measures; access control and AI thermal cameras; and space sterilization deodorizers. The company also engages in the ATM management and call center business; and provision of designated management, insurance agency, building maintenance, and real estate brokerage activities. In addition, it is involved in the purchase, sale, and rental and lease of automated external ED systems; sale of construction equipment; and provision of sterilization and disinfection services for corporate companies, as well as air catalyst coating services. Toyo Tec Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1966 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan.
